// navigation
header.mdl-layout__header.mdl-layout__header--waterfall.portfolio-header
  .mdl-layout__header-row.portfolio-logo-row
    span.mdl-layout__title
      .portfolio-logo
      span.mdl-layout__title Simple portfolio website
  .mdl-layout__header-row.portfolio-navigation-row.mdl-layout--large-screen-only
    nav.mdl-navigation.mdl-typography--body-1-force-preferred-font
      a.mdl-navigation__link.is-active(href='index.html') About
      a.mdl-navigation__link(href='blog.html') Blog
      a.mdl-navigation__link(href='gallery.html') Portfolio
      a.mdl-navigation__link(href='resume.html') Resume
.mdl-layout__drawer.mdl-layout--small-screen-only
  nav.mdl-navigation.mdl-typography--body-1-force-preferred-font
    a.mdl-navigation__link.is-active(href='index.html') About
    a.mdl-navigation__link(href='blog.html') Blog
    a.mdl-navigation__link(href='gallery.html') Portfolio
    a.mdl-navigation__link(href='resume.html') Resume
// content
main.mdl-layout__content
  .mdl-grid.portfolio-max-width.portfolio-contact
    .mdl-cell.mdl-cell--12-col.mdl-card.mdl-shadow--4dp
      .mdl-card__title
        h2.mdl-card__title-text Contact
      .mdl-card__media
        img.article-image(src=' images/contact-image.jpg', border='0', alt='')
      .mdl-card__supporting-text
        p
          | Enim labore aliqua consequat ut quis ad occaecat aliquip incididunt. Sunt nulla eu enim irure enim nostrud aliqua consectetur ad consectetur sunt ullamco officia. Ex officia laborum et consequat duis.
        p
          | Excepteur reprehenderit sint exercitation ipsum consequat qui sit id velit elit. Velit anim eiusmod labore sit amet.
        form(action='#')
          .mdl-textfield.mdl-js-textfield.mdl-textfield--floating-label
            input#Name.mdl-textfield__input(pattern='[A-Z,a-z, ]*', type='text')
            label.mdl-textfield__label(for='Name') Name...
            span.mdl-textfield__error Letters and spaces only
          .mdl-textfield.mdl-js-textfield.mdl-textfield--floating-label
            input#Email.mdl-textfield__input(type='text')
            label.mdl-textfield__label(for='Email') Email...
          .mdl-textfield.mdl-js-textfield.mdl-textfield--floating-label
            textarea#note.mdl-textfield__input(type='text', rows='5')
            label.mdl-textfield__label(for='note') Enter note
          p
            button.mdl-button.mdl-js-button.mdl-button--raised.mdl-js-ripple-effect.mdl-button--accent(type='submit')
              | Submit
  footer.mdl-mini-footer
    .mdl-mini-footer__left-section
      .mdl-logo Simple portfolio website
    .mdl-mini-footer__right-section
      ul.mdl-mini-footer__link-list
        li
          a(href='#') Help
        li
          a(href='#') Privacy & Terms
script(src='https://code.getmdl.io/1.2.0/material.min.js')
